reviews.text: 喺呢區食左成兩年lunch都無為意呢間小店，同事推介，就試試午餐set啦！
牛扒是我最愛的，咖啡也很香濃，大街中英味西餐的選擇，價錢中上值得推介.
非常道地的西餐，酒也是上選，會想ㄧ來再來。
中高級價錢，食物質素足5星，有高級餐廳質素，無高級餐廳環境，員工友善，街坊感覺，沒有高級餐廳的拘謹，值得一去再去！
我去完長隆後，在這裡慶祝母親節吃大餐

reviews.text: Decent local shop for marinated duck. Local local

A Local restaurant with so-so food quality and poor service. I have been here multiple times because it's a convenient location for me and they serve one of my favorite dishes,marinated ducks, not that they are great at making it. Food is ok and will fill your tummy at decent value. Expect attitude problems at times.
French Toast is very nice here. They have regular and cheese filling favor, I've tried the regular one, it's different to the other hk restaurant.
Ok

A neighborhood gem. "Hole in the wall" cafe has nice beef and wonton noodles combined with side dishes of duck and layered pork. Lady owner is very friendly and customers are her long time local residents
